\begin_inset Formula $sA$
\end_inset

) minus the depreciation rate of physical capital (
\begin_inset Formula $ùõø$
\end_inset

) should be greater than the constant population growth rate (
\begin_inset Formula $n).$
\end_inset


\end_layout

